VICCP 2 CORE Trailer 1

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2324220/VICCP_2_Core/

The Very Important Central Control Panel is back. Keeping the mysterious atmosphere and with even more mysteries. Control the omnipotence remote, experiment, and find many endings. Brainstorming in retro sci-fi style / Puzzle / Quest / Point Click.
